Easy Binary Search Problems

Start with these to get comfortable with the basic template.

   X 704. Binary Search – Classic binary search in a sorted array.

   X 278. First Bad Version – Find the first occurrence in a range.

   X 35. Search Insert Position – Find position to insert.

   X 367. Valid Perfect Square – Square root using binary search.

   X 69. Sqrt(x) – Integer square root.

   X 852. Peak Index in a Mountain Array – Binary search for the peak.

   X 744. Find Smallest Letter Greater Than Target – Circular search.

   X 374. Guess Number Higher or Lower – Binary search with feedback.

Medium Binary Search Problems

Once basics are clear, move to slightly more challenging variations.

    X 34. Find First and Last Position of Element in Sorted Array – Binary search for boundaries.

    X 162. Find Peak Element – Binary search in an unsorted array.

    X 33. Search in Rotated Sorted Array – Binary search with rotation.

    X 81. Search in Rotated Sorted Array II – Rotation + duplicates.

    X 153. Find Minimum in Rotated Sorted Array – Minimum in rotated array.

    XXX 154. Find Minimum in Rotated Sorted Array II – Same but with duplicates.

    287. Find the Duplicate Number – Binary search on value range.

    540. Single Element in a Sorted Array – Pair index trick.

    4. Median of Two Sorted Arrays – Partition logic (harder side of medium).

    222. Count Complete Tree Nodes – Binary search on tree height.
